high_descs: Turn around and come out of the bedroom and walk straight and enter into the study room.
Take the mug from the top of the table.
Turn your right and come out of the study room and enter into the kitchen which is in your right side and then walk towards the microwave.
Open the oven and then keep the mug inside of the oven and close the door. After some time, open the oven and take the mug out.
Turn back and move towards the countertop.
Place the mug on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Place the Mug on the CounterTop

high_descs: Head rotate the bedroom and turn right to the desk.
Pick the mug from the table and walk towards the wall.
Turn right and turn left towards the microwave.
Turn left and walk near the mug.
Place the cup inside the countertop microwave and pick it back.
Turn left on the countertop and place the mug on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Place the mug on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the desk.
Take the mug from the table.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the mug into the microwave oven.
Then take it out from the countertop microwave oven.
Put the mug on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Heated and placed the mug on the countertop.
